    <div class="tool-item"><div class="tool-name">pH Testing Strips</div><div class="tool-use">Test your DIY recipes (target 4.5–5.5 for hair health)</div></div>
  </div>

  <div class="col-label" style="margin:28px 0 16px;">UPGRADE WHEN POSSIBLE</div>
  <div class="tools-grid">
    <div class="tool-item"><div class="tool-name">Huetiful Hair Steamer</div><div class="tool-use">Superior to hooded dryer for deep conditioning — moist heat is more effective than dry heat for high porosity</div></div>
